      • setAcquisitionModules

        public boolean setAcquisitionModules(Collection<? extends AcquisitionDevice> selectedModules)
        Set the visible acquisition devices. All devices in the given set will be made visible, and all others will be removed.
        Parameters:
        selectedModules - The acquisition devices to show
        Returns:
        True if the device selection changes as a result of this invocation, false otherwise

      • addAcquisitionModule

        public boolean addAcquisitionModule(AcquisitionDevice module)
        Set an acquisition device to be visible. All currently visible devices will remain so.
        Parameters:
        module - The acquisition device to show
        Returns:
        True if the device selection changes as a result of this invocation, false otherwise

      • removeAcquisitionModule

        public boolean removeAcquisitionModule(AcquisitionDevice module)
        Set an acquisition device to not be visible. All other currently visible devices will remain so.
        Parameters:
        module - The acquisition device to not show
        Returns:
        True if the device selection changes as a result of this invocation, false otherwise
